headline: Trimble and TDK Join Forces to Accelerate Precision Navigation
summary: Trimble® and InvenSense, a TDK group company, today announced they will work together to deliver an advanced navigation solution that combines the Trimble ProPoint® Go engine and Trimble RTX® correction service with TDK's SmartAutomotive™ Inertial Measurement Units (IMUs) module from InvenSense. Customers can now take advantage of greater accuracy and reliability in positioning and navigation across various automotive and IoT applications.

headline: How Is Trimble's Stock Performance Compared to Other Technology Stocks?
summary: Trimble has outperformed relative to its technology peers over the past year, and Wall Street analysts maintain a strongly optimistic view on the stock’s outlook.
